WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.480
In general, I've always optimized for learning and impact, and so if I feel like I can make

00:00:06.480 --> 00:00:11.560
a change in my career and position myself in some place where I can have more impact

00:00:11.560 --> 00:00:17.320
or I'm learning or exposed to new things, then that will help me grow.

00:00:17.320 --> 00:00:23.160
I've also been very motivated by relationships and the people that I work with, and so surrounding

00:00:23.160 --> 00:00:29.139
yourself with people, people that share your values, people that inspire you, is really

00:00:29.139 --> 00:00:33.020
really important to help you grow and develop in your career.

00:00:33.020 --> 00:00:39.540
And so I always give the advice to, especially people earlier in their career, to focus on

00:00:39.540 --> 00:00:44.740
building relationships and working with people who are a lot more experienced than you or

00:00:44.740 --> 00:00:49.820
people that you feel like you can learn from and learn their tricks and use that to help

00:00:49.820 --> 00:00:50.380
you get better.

